xists in `docs/` but does not appear in the site menu.\n\n**Solution:** Add the page to the `nav` section of `mkdocs.yml`.\n\n## Validation Script Reports Errors\n\n**Symptom:** `make validate` prints errors and exits with a non-zero code.\n\n**Solution:** Read the error message carefully. It will list missing files or malformed configuration. Fix the reported issue and re-run the script.\n\n## Theme Not Loading\n\n**Symptom:** The site renders with plain HTML and no styling.\n\n**Solution:** Install the theme with `pip install mkdocs-material` and ensure `theme.name: material` is set in `mkdocs.yml`.\n"}], "message": "Add troubleshooting documentation and include it in MkDocs navigation\n\n- Add Troubleshooting entry to mkdocs.yml nav\n- Expand docs/troubleshooting.md with common issues and solutions\n\nAddresses issue #3", "owner": "rpnr-bench", "repo": "T16_R01_C02_A02"}, "id": "call_15b3605fc84c488da8d8ff21", "type": "tool_call"}], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 9006, "output_tokens": 747, "total_tokens": 9753, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 8576}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 253}}}}]}}}
